* And all the other boys...

31:52.210 --> 31:53.404
No, no, no.

31:53.440 --> 31:55.374
It's not what you think.
Fantasia!

31:55.410 --> 31:58.140
She's gone,
she let me in.

31:58.180 --> 31:59.977
You need to go.

