said you were married in court.

32:02.120 --> 32:03.212
Well, I was married.

32:03.250 --> 32:04.581
I wanted to yell
right there.

32:04.620 --> 32:05.985
Why?

32:06.020 --> 32:07.282
'Cause...

32:07.320 --> 32:08.548
