33:01.780 --> 33:03.600
Thank you, God,
for all your blessings.

33:03.640 --> 33:06.074
Thank you for tonight
and for being with friends.

33:06.110 --> 33:09.216
And for stimulating
conversation.

33:09.250 --> 33:12.617
And for your great Word.

33:12.650 --> 33:15.585
We're especially thankful
tonight for Grace.

33:15.620 --> 33:18.282
She has done
something extraordinary

33:18.330 --> 33:20.582
in the last 24 hours, Jesus.

33:20.630 --> 33:23.019
She has reached her mother.

