33:29.300 --> 33:31.609
So I want us all
to take Grace's example

33:31.640 --> 33:34.131
and never give up
on our loved ones.

33:34.180 --> 33:35.533
Thank you, Grace.

33:35.580 --> 33:37.605
In Jesus' name we pray.
Amen.

33:37.640 --> 33:39.608
ALL:
Amen.

33:39.650 --> 33:42.210
So what did you say, Grace,
that made your mom listen?

33:42.250 --> 33:44.514
Um, well, you know,
she's still struggling.

33:44.550 --> 33:46.438
We all are.

33:46.490 --> 33:49.516
The important thing is she
opened the door even an inch.

33:49.560 --> 33:52.757
And you opened
that door.

33:56.600 --> 33:57.692
DIANE:
Hello, gentlemen.

33:57.730 --> 34:00.392
How'd you get past reception?

34:00.430 --> 34:02.068
I let them in.
