34:02.100 --> 34:03.533
I'm here about my lease.

34:03.570 --> 34:04.707
Page 24, paragraph 18D.

34:04.740 --> 34:06.537
(David chuckles)

34:06.570 --> 34:08.629
You thinkjust showing up
counts as physical presence?

34:08.680 --> 34:10.568
There's not a court
in the land...

34:10.610 --> 34:13.704
Actually, no. We're talking
about paragraph 18D.

34:13.750 --> 34:16.173
If the leaseholder
is unable to be

34:16.220 --> 34:17.642
physically on the premises,

34:17.680 --> 34:19.147
said obligation
may be fulfilled

34:19.190 --> 34:21.158
by his or her proxy.

34:21.190 --> 34:22.555
Say hello to his

34:22.590 --> 34:23.784
or her proxy.

34:23.820 --> 34:25.651
You hired him?

34:25.690 --> 34:27.851
