should you need me.

34:37.140 --> 34:38.368
KALINDA:
HI.

34:38.410 --> 34:39.365
Kalinda, anything on
the other apps?

34:39.410 --> 34:40.707
ELSBETH:
Hi, Kalinda.

34:40.740 --> 34:42.628
It's Elsbeth, too.
KALINDA: Hi, Elsbeth.

34:42.680 --> 34:45.740
No, um, nothing with
any kind of decryption code.

34:45.780 --> 34:48.419
But, in 2002,
the same Chinese company

34:48.450 --> 34:49.872
bought a firewall program

34:49.920 --> 34:52.741
from a Boston firm by the name
