34:52.790 --> 34:54.212
Cunneyworth? What is that?

34:54.260 --> 34:55.818
It's a CIA front company.

34:55.860 --> 34:57.748
You're kidding.

34:57.790 --> 34:59.621
No. They had to close shop

34:59.660 --> 35:01.651
a few months later
after their name appeared

35:01.700 --> 35:04.191
in news_stories about_
the Valerie Plame affair.

35:04.230 --> 35:05.720
ALICIA: Okay, well,
we can argue double standard,

35:05.770 --> 35:07.897
that the US. government
did the same thing

35:07.930 --> 35:09.761
they're accusing J-Serve of.
ELSBETH:
Do you have any documentation?

35:09.800 --> 35:11.904
I'm trying to get my hands
on an invoice,

35:11.940 --> 35:13.828
but it's gonna take some time.
ALICIA:
We'll ask for a further delay.

35:13.870 --> 35:16.338
KALIN DA: Okay.
No.

35:18.480 --> 35:19.674
Yes, Elsbeth?

35:19.710 --> 35:21.177
No.

35:21.220 --> 35:22.642
I think there might be
another way.

35:22.680 --> 35:24.682
What other way?

35:24.720 --> 35:27.484
I've got his buttons.

35:27.520 --> 35:28.509
(phone beeps)

35:36.960 --> 35:38.666
Are you all right?

35:38.700 --> 35:40.395
Yeah. Why?

35:40.430 --> 35:42.239
I heard about last night.

35:42.270 --> 35:44.158
Yeah. 800 yards into Indiana,
and I'm a felon again.

35:44.210 --> 35:45.563
Well, we're here
for you, Cary.

35:45.610 --> 35:48.636
I know we've had
our differences about work,

35:48.680 --> 35:51.205
but anything you need,
we're here.

35:51.250 --> 35:52.945
I think it's best I
take a break from work.

35:52.980 --> 35:54.470
No.

35:54.520 --> 35:55.669
Alicia, they're
coming after me,

35:55.720 --> 35:57.711
and whatever I do,
I'm an anvil here.

35:57.750 --> 35:59.547
No.

35:59.590 --> 36:01.808
We do this together.

36:01.860 --> 36:03.919
(sighs)

36:03.960 --> 36:05.848
Okay.

36:07.760 --> 36:09.728
After further interviews,
this officer concludes

36:09.760 --> 36:12.695
that the bail infraction
was inadvertent.

36:12.730 --> 36:17.690
But the officer also concludes
that Mr. Agos has been

36:17.740 --> 36:21.437
casual in his conformity
to judicial rulings.

36:21.480 --> 36:24.574
Therefore, we advise
further restrictions on bail.

36:24.610 --> 36:26.771
What restrictions?

36:26.810 --> 36:28.744
Ankle monitoring bracelet

36:28.780 --> 36:30.668
and a 9:00 curfew.

36:30.720 --> 36:33.484
Your Honor, lawyer hours would
make this highly impractical.

36:33.520 --> 36:35.249
That's unfortunate.
I don't care.

36:35.290 --> 36:36.450
What else, Ms. Grubick?

36:36.490 --> 36:39.948
No contact with
the firm investigator

36:39.990 --> 36:41.799
Kalinda Sharma.

36:41.830 --> 36:44.321
I'm sorry, what?
Uh, 725 ILCS

36:44.370 --> 36:48.932
185 prohibits interaction with
anyone considered dangerous.

36:48.970 --> 36:50.528
JUDGE:
Why is she dangerous?

36:50.570 --> 36:51.832
Prior arrests,

36:51.870 --> 36:56.273
a grand jury charge
and contact with Lemond Bishop.

36:56.310 --> 36:58.346
DIANE: This is unacceptable,
Your Honor. Ms. Sharma is

36:58.380 --> 37:01.008
an integral part of the
operation of Mr. Agos's firm.

37:01.050 --> 37:05.589
Yes, and Kalinda Sharma works
closely on Mr. Agos's cases,

37:05.620 --> 37:08.783
as well as being
a social, uh, acquaintance,

37:08.820 --> 37:12.824
but my report advises that the
court's rulings are paramount.

37:12.860 --> 37:14.828
JUDGE: ASA Polmar, do you agree
with these added restrictions?

37:14.860 --> 37:16.748
We do, Your Honor.
All right.

37:16.800 --> 37:18.392
The bail is approved,

37:18.430 --> 37:20.022
but only with these
further restrictions applying.

37:20.070 --> 37:22.391
And if you break the rules
again, young man,

37:22.440 --> 37:23.759
your bail will be revoked,

37:23.800 --> 37:25.028
and you'll spend the
rest of your time

37:25.070 --> 37:26.765
until trial behind bars.

37:32.810 --> 37:34.778
(door opens)
Hi.

37:34.820 --> 37:36.811
(chuckles):
Hi.

37:43.320 --> 37:45.288
Here are your buttons.
Oh. (chuckles)

37:45.330 --> 37:48.299
Thank you.
Oh, and here...

37:48.330 --> 37:50.821
is one of yours I found
in my hair this morning.

37:50.860 --> 37:52.669
(chuckles)

37:52.700 --> 37:56.295
That song's been
in my head.

37:56.340 --> 37:56.931
Mm...

37:56.970 --> 37:58.562
Actually, I'm here for work.

37:58.610 --> 37:59.861
Oh.

37:59.910 --> 38:02.071
One of our investigators,
Kalinda Sharma,

38:02.110 --> 38:06.900
found an invoice from
a CIA shell company

38:06.950 --> 38:09.009
that sold firewall software

38:09.050 --> 38:10.915
to everyone's favorite
Chinese company.

38:10.950 --> 38:14.716
I think the judge would love to
hear how the Justice Department

38:14.760 --> 38:16.387
is selectively prosecuting us.

38:16.420 --> 38:20.652
Mm. I take it you have an
original invoice as proof.

38:20.690 --> 38:22.328
I do indeed.

38:22.360 --> 38:23.918
Huh.

38:23.960 --> 38:27.964
How do I know you're not faking?

38:39.710 --> 38:40.699
Uh-huh.

38:40.750 --> 38:42.775
Well...

38:44.720 --> 38:46.745
Yeah.

38:46.790 --> 38:48.917
(Elsbeth gasps,
shredder whirring)

38:48.960 --> 38:50.916
That was evidence!

38:50.960 --> 38:51.927
Yes.

38:51.960 --> 38:53.518
And now it's gone.

38:53.560 --> 38:55.619
What you just did is illegal.

38:55.660 --> 38:57.696
No, what you think I
just did was illegal.

38:57.730 --> 38:59.095
You just dropped it
in your shredder.

38:59.130 --> 39:01.894
(sighs) Yes. I'm sorry.

39:01.940 --> 39:05.535
So... last night
didn't matter to you?

39:05.570 --> 39:07.037
It did.

39:07.070 --> 39:08.435
But work is work.

39:10.080 --> 39:15.677
So you are fully aware that
you just destroyed evidence,

39:15.720 --> 39:20.043
Assistant United States Attorney
Josh Perotti,

39:20.090 --> 39:21.887
at 9:47 am.

39:21.920 --> 39:23.615
Nice try, Elsbeth.

39:23.660 --> 39:25.389
But that recording
is inadmissible.

39:25.430 --> 39:27.057
It requires
two-party consent.

39:27.090 --> 39:29.854
Well, then you need to spend
more time in Illinois

39:29.900 --> 39:33.165
and less in DC, because
this state's Supreme Court

39:33.200 --> 39:36.169
recently struck down
the two-party consent law.

39:36.200 --> 39:39.033
I only need one party.

39:39.070 --> 39:40.833
And that's me.

39:40.870 --> 39:44.806
And I, oh... I consent.

39:46.810 --> 39:48.448
(phone beeps)

39:51.590 --> 39:54.559
So... call me.

39:54.590 --> 39:56.581
Maybe.

40:02.160 --> 40:04.799
Are you sure about this,
Mr. Perotti?
Yes, Your Honor.

40:04.830 --> 40:07.628
We are withdrawing all charges
against J-Serve

40:07.670 --> 40:08.932
and Camilla Vargas.

40:08.970 --> 40:11.188
The Justice Department
considers this matter closed.

40:11.240 --> 40:12.605
JUDGE:
Okay, then.

40:12.640 --> 40:15.131
This was a supreme waste
of time.

40:15.180 --> 40:16.909
(gavelbangs)
In your opinion?

40:16.940 --> 40:18.771
CAMILLA:
Thank you, both.

40:18.810 --> 40:21.973
Now we can go back to suing you
for $23 million.

40:22.020 --> 40:23.908
Oh, I can't wait.

40:23.950 --> 40:25.486
See you in court.

40:34.830 --> 40:36.798
You shouldn't have done it.

40:36.830 --> 40:37.956
You shouldn't
have either.

40:38.000 --> 40:40.889
Are you heading out?

40:40.930 --> 40:43.990
Yeah, back to DC.

40:44.040 --> 40:46.167
Bye, Elsbeth.

40:48.210 --> 40:49.871
Good-bye, Josh.

40:58.120 --> 41:00.543
(sniffing)

41:01.290 --> 41:03.212
(elevator bell dings)

41:07.930 --> 41:09.921
You've got to
be kidding me.

41:13.070 --> 41:15.038
DIANE: Well, the first order
of business

41:15.070 --> 41:16.594
is replacing that.

41:24.950 --> 41:27.976
They removed
the "F," the "A," and the "L."

41:28.010 --> 41:29.216
Subﬂe.

41:29.250 --> 41:30.911
(laughs)

41:36.690 --> 41:39.659
Well, Cary says he's fine
with David Lee's office,

41:39.690 --> 41:41.658
so I guess this
is you and me.

41:51.840 --> 41:54.968
No, take mine.

41:55.010 --> 41:57.228
No, Diane.

41:59.810 --> 42:01.209
I could use
a fresh start.

42:01.250 --> 42:04.742
You take my office.

42:04.790 --> 42:07.042
I won't hear of it.

